author: news.com.au
title: Ruby Rose coming back to Sydney for a Mardi Gras appearance where girlfriend Jess is performing
text:
HOLLYWOOD’S new darling, Ruby Rose, is to jet into the country this week. 
The Aussie model-turned-actress, who is taking a break from filming two feature films in the US — shark epic Meg and comedy Pitch Perfect 3 — is due to touch down midweek ahead of a Mardi Gras appearance and a gig with the ROVA selfie flying camera.
Ruby Rose is coming home for Mardi Gras to celebrate and see her girlfriend Jess perform. Picture: Frederic J. Brown Source: AFP 
Rose will attend the Mardi Gras on March 4, where her girlfriend Jess Origliasso — one half of Aussie pop duo The Veronicas — is performing.
The pair rekindled their romance in November last year after they reconnected while filming a video clip for The Veronicas single On Your Side.
Rose will also be the guest of honour at an official ROVA drone launch party on March 6 at 
Luke Mangan’s Glass Brasserie at the Hilton.
RELATED: RUBY AND JESS SHARE INTIMATE LACY LINGERIE SNAP 
The loved-up pair revealed on Instagram they were dating late last year. Picture: Instagram Source: Instagram 
It’s a happy homecoming for Rose, who last month revealed she was unemployed for two years after moving to the United States.
“There was no manager that believed I would be able to do acting, no agents,” she said.
Originally published as Ruby coming home for Mardi Gras
